2.5 Throwing and catching exceptions in Kotlin
	- Kotlin doesnt' have "new" keyword.

	- If the throw construct is an exrepssion, and can be used as a part of other expressions:
		ex)
			================================================================================
			val percentage = if(number in 0..100){
				number
			}else{
				throw IllegalArgumentException("
					A percentage value must be between 0 and 100: $number
				")
			}
			================================================================================